HEADWORD: Hempen
<hw>Hemp"en</hw> <pr>(-'n)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Made of
hemp; <as>as, a <ex>hempen</ex> cord</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Like hemp.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Beat into a
<xex>hempen</xex> state.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Cook.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hempy</ent>⟦br⟧
